snippet.title: Spyragon: Builder Bash
snippet.description:
Spyragon is available to play on the iOS App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/spyragon/id1584715775

Builder is one of the most powerful tools in the Spyragon Classic toolbox.  Use it to leverage extra rotations to create larger Stars, Combos, and Full Hexagons.  See some brilliant examples of how Builder can help advance your Spyragon gameplay!

Directions available at: https://spyraverse.com

Also follow us on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter: @spyraverse
